com.gams.api

Enum GAMSGlobals.DebugLevel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<GAMSGlobals.DebugLevel>
      • com.gams.api.GAMSGlobals.DebugLevel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<GAMSGlobals.DebugLevel>
    Enclosing class:
    GAMSGlobals

    public static enum GAMSGlobals.DebugLevel
extends java.lang.Enum<GAMSGlobals.DebugLevel>
    Define GAMS Debug Level of different values and string representations. When a GAMSWorkspace instance is created, it also allows an environment variable "GAMSOOAPIDEBUG" containing a String representing the DebugLevel to override the debug level that has been set from either a GAMSWorkspaceInfo instance or a String instance parameter of a {GAMSWorkspace} constructor.
    See Also:
    GAMSWorkspace, GAMSWorkspaceInfo

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      KEEP_FILES
      = 1 with string representation "keepfiles", Keep temporary files
      OFF
      = 0 with string representation "off", No Debug
      SHOW_LOG
      = 2 with string representation "showlog", Send GAMS log to standard output and keep temporary files
      UNDEFINED_LEVEL
      >= 4 with string representation "undefined", Undefined variable type
      VERBOSE
      = 3 with string representation "verbose", Send highly technical info and GAMS log to standard output and keep temporary file
